data.title: About: R. Kannan
data.meta_description: R. Kannan (born Rajmohan on 21 July 1971) is an Indian filmmaker. He made his directorial debut with the successful Tamil film Jayamkondaan starring Vinay Rai and Bhavana in 2008.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

R. Kannan (nama lahir Rajmohan lahir 21 Juli 1971) adalah seorang pembuat film asal India. Ia membuat debut penyutradaraannya dengan film Tamil sukses yang dibintangi oleh dan pada 2008. (in)

R. Kannan (born Rajmohan on 21 July 1971) is an Indian filmmaker. He made his directorial debut with the successful Tamil film Jayamkondaan starring Vinay Rai and Bhavana in 2008. (en)
